name: SpineOrNeckDisorderSNOMEDCT
title: Spine or Neck Disorder SNOMED CT
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Spinal neuropathy, neck or back injuries and fractures, neck or muscle atrophy, and spine or neck disorders such as kyphosis, lordosis, scoliosis, spinal osteochrondrosis and spondylitis, and history of spinal surgeries.),(Data Element Scope: Conditions related to the spine and neck that may qualify a patient for spinal orthotics as defined by U.S. Centers for Medicare and Medicaid.),(Inclusion Criteria: Spinal neuropathy, neck or back injuries and fractures, neck or muscle atrophy, and spine or neck disorders such as kyphosis, lordosis, scoliosis, spinal osteochrondrosis and spondylitis, and history of spinal surgeries.),(Exclusion Criteria: Superficial injuries to the spine and neck.)
